Global Lighting Fixtures Market Insights
Lighting Fixtures Market size was valued at USD 100 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 150 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6% from 2024 to 2030.

Lighting Fixtures Market Overview
The global lighting fixtures market is anticipated to witness significant growth, valued at approximately USD 70.3 billion in 2024, with a projected CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is attributed to the increasing demand for energy-efficient lighting solutions, technological advancements in smart lighting systems, and the growing trend of interior and architectural lighting innovations. The market is driven by both residential and commercial sectors, where energy savings and sustainability are primary considerations. With the rise of smart homes and commercial spaces seeking enhanced aesthetics and functionality, the lighting fixtures market is poised to expand rapidly.

